  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK860">
<l>ikalāṉā miṉṉāta vellā nakalāṉā </l>
<l>naṉṉaya meṉṉuñ cerukku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All calamities are caused by hatred but by the delight (of friendship) is caused the great wealth of good virtues.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
